---

title: 女中才是真女王
layout: post
permalink: /女中才是真女王

---

<img width="100%" src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/OcEogMl0K3icAF88d5DUFQkQJ0qwoovL6FicTDqocHLEO7soajfL9w2Z6ZJuQYZkMQL4a2CRuFictVH7ia932RtqrQ/0">

<hr style="font-family:宋体;" />
<p style="font-family:宋体;">
    <span style="font-size:16px;color:#262626;">征服了荆棘音高与碎石节奏的女中，才有资格滴蜡烛甩皮鞭！</span>
</p>
<hr style="font-family:宋体;" />

<p style="font-family:宋体;text-align:center;">
    <strong><span style="font-size:20px;">女中才是真女王</span></strong>
</p>

<p style="font-family:宋体;text-align:center;">
    <span style="font-size:14px;color:#595959;">翻译：方诗</span><br />
</p>
<p style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;text-align:center;">
    <span style="font-family:宋体,simsun;font-size:14px;orphans:2;widows:2;color:#595959;">人文爱乐合唱团女中音</span><br />
</p>
<p style="font-family:宋体;">
    <br />
</p>
<p>
    <span style="font-family:tahoma;orphans:2;text-align:-webkit-auto;widows:2;font-size:16px;">　　女中都是地球上口味最咸的人，至少她们自己如此认为。其实女中都是随性的女汉子，完全不介意穿牛仔裤而不是黑色窗帘布去卖唱～</span>
</p>
<p>
    <br />
</p>
<p>
    <span style="font-family:tahoma;orphans:2;text-align:-webkit-auto;widows:2;font-size:16px;">　　女中声部在合唱团中处在一个不能抱怨音太高或者太低的微妙位置，因此其他声部都认为女中最容易唱，然而女中深知事实并非如此。在女高卖力爬到High A的床沿时，没人听见女中在纠结成片成片的升降号与恶作剧般的节奏，因为女高叫得太响（男低常常也是），所以女中鲜为人知的极大乐趣之一，就是把女高扯下床～</span>
</p>
<p>
    <span style="font-family:tahoma;orphans:2;text-align:-webkit-auto;widows:2;font-size:medium;"><br />
    </span>
</p>
<p>
    <span style="font-family:tahoma;orphans:2;text-align:-webkit-auto;widows:2;font-size:16px;">　　至于男高这个与女中唱着几乎相同音域的声部，女中从来就没信任过这些不解风情的呆瓜。她们喜欢男低，因为只有在与男低二重唱时，女中才能被听到，男低就是一列鼓风机！</span>
</p>
<p>
    <span style="font-family:tahoma;orphans:2;text-align:-webkit-auto;widows:2;font-size:medium;"><br />
    </span>
</p>
<p>
    <span style="font-family:tahoma;orphans:2;text-align:-webkit-auto;widows:2;font-size:16px;">　　女中的另外一个烦恼是，常常因为声部内人太多，而不得不每个人都唱得很小声！</span>
</p>
<p>
    <br />
</p>
<p>
    <br />
</p>
<p>
    <strong><span style="font-family:tahoma;orphans:2;text-align:-webkit-auto;widows:2;font-size:medium;">成为女中十个原因</span></strong><span style="font-family:tahoma;orphans:2;text-align:-webkit-auto;widows:2;font-size:medium;"><br />
    </span>
</p>
<p>
    <span style="font-family:tahoma;orphans:2;text-align:-webkit-auto;widows:2;font-size:medium;"><br />
    </span>
</p>
<p style="font-size:16px;">
    1. 女中擅长唱降E<br />
    2. 以降E为G点，女中可以连续高潮12个小节<br />
    3. 还不用前戏<br />
    4. 即使整个合唱团很稀烂，女中也不大可能会被喷<br />
    5. 女高solo时，女中有大把时间互相调情<br />
    6. 面对那些从来不研究谱子只知道女高的外行人，女中总是用她们比女高优秀的事实来粉碎他们的偏见<br />
    7. 有时可以干干男高的活<br />
    8<span style="color:#3e3e3e;font-family:宋体, simsun;line-height:32px;background-color:#ffffff;"></span>. 对女中，休止总是很充足的<br />
    9. 当女高在尾声叫破了喉咙，只有女中从容享受到最后<br />
    10. 叫我女王大人！<br />
</p>
<p style="font-family:宋体;">
    <br />
</p>
<p style="font-family:宋体;">
    <br />
</p>
<hr style="font-family:宋体;" />
<p style="font-family:宋体;">
    <br />
</p>
<p style="font-size:medium;text-align:-webkit-auto;font-family:tahoma;orphans:2;widows:2;">
    <strong>Top Ten Reasons for Being an Alto</strong>
</p>
<p style="font-size:medium;text-align:-webkit-auto;font-family:tahoma;orphans:2;widows:2;">
    <strong><br />
    </strong>
</p>
<p>
    1. You get really good at singing E flat.
</p>
<p>
    2. You get to sing the same note for 12 consecutive measures.
</p>
<p>
    3. You don&#39;t really need to warm up to sing 12 consecutive bars of E-flat.
</p>
<p>
    4. If the choir really stinks, it&#39;s unlikely the altos will be blamed.
</p>
<p>
    5. You have lots of time to chat during soprano solos.
</p>
<p>
    6. You get to pretend that you are better than the sopranos, because everybody knows that women only sing soprano so they don&#39;t have to learn to read music.
</p>
<p>
    7. You can sometimes find part time work singing tenor.
</p>
<p>
    8. Altos get all the great intervals.
</p>
<p>
    9. When the sopranos are holding some outrageously high note at the end of a song, the altos always get the last words.
</p>
<p>
    10. When the altos miss a note, nobody gets hurt.
</p>
<p style="font-family:宋体;">
    <br />
</p><span style="font-size:16px;color:#595959;"></span>
<p>
    <br />
</p>
